/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling highway in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, providing a driver's eye view of the scene. The highway, divided by a median, stretches out ahead, flanked by lush greenery on one side and towering buildings on the other. The sky overhead is a blanket of overcast clouds, casting a soft light over the scene. In the distance, the faint outline of mountains can be seen, adding a touch of natural beauty to the urban landscape. The colors in the image are predominantly green and gray, reflecting the blend of nature and architecture that characterizes Beijing.
